1
00:00:00,600 --> 00:00:02,400
Saki Mizuguchi.

2
00:00:02,400 --> 00:00:05,900
I will take her.

3
00:00:07,180 --> 00:00:10,520
Will you start over with me?

4
00:00:10,520 --> 00:00:12,720
This time with marriage in mind.

5
00:00:18,700 --> 00:00:21,000
I'm sorry,

6
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:24,400
you probably can't think about that stuff yet, huh?

7
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:28,800
When you're ready to open your heart again,

8
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:31,890
please let me ask you again.

9
00:00:31,890 --> 00:00:38,500
